messages.message: Custom functions should be available as well for internal users, you have to enable it in settings

> Will Clean Custom Functions be released Monday along with Prompts?
to extend Arjun’s answer above
• Custom Functions in Clean will be available to commercial internal users only, and you have to enable it in your user settings to see the feature
• Prompts in Clean will be available to all commercial users (both internal and external)

Also looking into other ways to provide more in-product tips/guidance in the near future cc @alagu in addition to onboarding materials that @Corey Brubaker is working on and documentation cc @melissa.amos
